那么你是来参加狂欢节的吗?

176
00:14:02,071 --> 00:14:05,114
Actually I'm just here to meet a girl.
事实上我是来这儿相亲的

177
00:14:05,221 --> 00:14:06,699
- Huh, a girl?  - Yes.
- 哈 泡妞啊?  - 是哦

178
00:14:06,912 --> 00:14:09,495
Little word of advice. You make the first move.
给你点忠告 你一定要主动出击

179
00:14:09,581 --> 00:14:12,582
- Brazilian women respond to confidence.  - Oh, right.
- 巴西女孩喜欢自信的男人  - 哦 没错

180
00:14:12,834 --> 00:14:14,625
Yes, it's all about swagger.
是啊 其实就是吹嘘

181
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:16,666
You've got to pop out that chest,
你一定要挺胸抬头

182
00:14:16,773 --> 00:14:18,374
swing that tail,
摇着尾巴

183
00:14:18,587 --> 00:14:22,159
eyes narrowed look like some kind of crazy love hawk.
微合双眼 发射出爱的火花 就像情圣一样

184
00:14:22,595 --> 00:14:24,928
- But first we've got to bust you out.  - What?
- 但是首先 我们要把你弄出这个笼子  - 什么?

185
00:14:24,972 --> 00:14:27,890
I'm gonna pop that cage open like a soda cap.
我开这笼子就像拔汽水罐一样易如反掌

186
00:14:28,267 --> 00:14:29,579
No, no...
不要 不要...

187
00:14:29,811 --> 00:14:31,310
No, no, that's okay.
不 不 真的不用

188
00:14:32,188 --> 00:14:33,958
You call that popping?
你管这叫拔?

189
00:14:34,232 --> 00:14:35,658
This thing's robust.
这玩意儿怪结实的

190
00:14:35,671 --> 00:14:37,775
No, no, guys, really, I'm fine. The cage is great.
不 不 伙计们 真的 我很好 这个笼子挺棒的

191
00:14:37,945 --> 00:14:39,048
Love the cage.
我很爱它

192
00:14:39,217 --> 00:14:40,675
Dabbo, suit yourself.
好吧 随便你吧

193
00:14:40,719 --> 00:14:42,906
Don't forget, love hawk.
别忘了 像个情圣

194
00:14:44,723 --> 00:14:48,016
Yes, yes and... and to you as well.
好好 嗯... 你们也是啊

195
00:14:49,416 --> 00:14:51,082
# Let me take you to Rio, Rio #
# 让我带你 走向里约 里约 #

196
00:14:54,014 --> 00:14:55,670
# And we can chillin' like a zebo #
# 欢笑阵阵 就如过节 过节 #

197
00:14:55,775 --> 00:14:57,503
里约热内卢 自然保护环境中心

198
00:14:57,872 --> 00:14:59,215
# Na na na #
# 呐呐呐 #

199
00:15:01,929 --> 00:15:04,721
This is the heart and soul of our aviary.
这是我们鸟舍的要地

200
00:15:04,891 --> 00:15:06,265
Our treatment room.
治疗室

201
00:15:08,019 --> 00:15:09,727
They really like you.
它们真的很喜欢你哦

202
00:15:11,606 --> 00:15:13,122
- A lot.  - Yes!
- 很喜欢  - 是啊!

203
00:15:13,128 --> 00:15:15,065
I'm their great big Mama Bird.
我就是他们伟大的鸟妈妈

204
00:15:22,326 --> 00:15:25,098
- You want some?  - Ah, oh, I'm good.
- 来点吗?  - 啊 哦 不用了

205
00:15:26,371 --> 00:15:29,163
Many of the birds here were rescued from smugglers.
这里大多数鸟都是从走私犯的手里救出来的

206
00:15:29,249 --> 00:15:31,311
- Smugglers?  - Yes.
- 走私贩?  - 是啊

207
00:15:31,482 --> 00:15:34,712
Unfortunately, the poor birds are often hurt.
不幸的是 这些可怜的鸟通常都受了伤

208
00:15:34,778 --> 00:15:36,277
or even killed in the process.
有些甚至会在走私的途中死掉

209
00:15:36,341 --> 00:15:39,133
But with proper care, they can be saved.
但是在精心照料下 它们很快就能好起来

210
00:15:39,427 --> 00:15:40,468
Look here.
看这儿

211
00:15:40,492 --> 00:15:42,471
This poor guy was found last night.
这只可怜的鸟是昨晚救回来的

212
00:15:44,079 --> 00:15:46,537
Hey, buddy, you're looking great today.
嘿 小家伙 你今天看起来不错

213
00:15:46,728 --> 00:15:48,852
Much better, much better.
好多了 好多了

214
00:15:50,731 --> 00:15:52,189
Get well soon.
祝你早日康复

215
00:15:54,695 --> 00:15:56,632
So, where is Jewel?
那么 珠儿在哪?

216
00:15:56,655 --> 00:15:58,884
Oh, we have a special place for Jewel.
哦 我们给她安排了一个特别的房间

217
00:15:58,907 --> 00:16:01,011
She's a very spirited bird.
她是只非常活泼的鸟

218
00:16:01,264 --> 00:16:02,763
I'll say.
没错

219
00:16:02,786 --> 00:16:04,306
She did that?
这是她干的?

220
00:16:04,496 --> 00:16:07,372
Charming. kay, I want to go home now.
真迷人啊 好了 我现在想回家了

221
00:16:07,688 --> 00:16:09,166
No, don't worry.
不 别担心

222
00:16:09,252 --> 00:16:11,814
I'm going to make you look irresistible.
我会把你打扮得帅到无可抗拒

223
00:16:17,364 --> 00:16:20,407
Help! Help! Let me out of here!
救命! 救命! 放我出去!

224
00:16:25,081 --> 00:16:26,580
Linda!
琳达!

225
00:16:26,666 --> 00:16:29,521
- Maybe I should...  - No, give it a chance.
- 或许我应该...  - 不 给他们个机会

226
00:16:40,119 --> 00:16:41,180
Hello?
有人吗?

227
00:16:43,851 --> 00:16:44,912
Hello?
有人吗?

228
00:16:47,690 --> 00:16:49,731
I come in peace.
我崇尚和平

229
00:16:54,988 --> 00:16:56,737
She's beautiful.
她真漂亮

230
00:16:59,806 --> 00:17:03,642
What were they talking about? She's... like an angel.
他们之前干嘛那么说啊? 她... 好像个天使

231
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:10,379
An angel whose getting really close up!
这天使离我越来越近了!

232
00:17:15,302 --> 00:17:18,761
- You're standing on my throat.  - You're an American.
- 你踩到我喉咙了  - 你是美国来的啊

233
00:17:19,432 --> 00:17:20,473
Thanks.
谢谢

234
00:17:20,474 --> 00:17:22,557
I need my throat for talking, so thank you.
我需要喉咙来说话 所以 多谢了

235
00:17:22,582 --> 00:17:24,040
You look like me.
你长得很像我

236
00:17:24,916 --> 00:17:25,998
Hi.
嗨

237
00:17:26,230 --> 00:17:27,896
Hi. My name is Blu.
嗨 我叫布鲁

238
00:17:28,066 --> 00:17:30,399
You know like the cheese with the mould on it.
你懂的 咱俩就像同一个印奶酪的模子刻出来的

239
00:17:30,444 --> 00:17:31,948
No, it smells really bad.
这个例子不好 奶酪闻起来很臭

240
00:17:31,951 --> 00:17:34,034
That's stupid, stupid, stupid.
真是笨呐 笨呐 笨呐

241
00:17:34,115 --> 00:17:36,469
Alright, come on, we don't have much time.
好吧 快点 我们时间不多

242
00:17:38,034 --> 00:17:39,658
Wait, wait, wait! Ouch!
等等 等等 等等! 嗷!

243
00:17:50,819 --> 00:17:52,464
- Are you ready?  - For what?
- 准备好了吗?  - 准备好什么?

244
00:17:52,614 --> 00:17:54,697
Oh, oh, wow. Aah... okay.
哦 哦 哇哦 啊... 好啊

245
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,615
Confidence!
自信!

246
00:17:56,931 --> 00:17:58,597
Crazy love hawk.
大情圣

247
00:18:01,310 --> 00:18:02,778
Wow, hey! What are you doing?
哇哦 嘿! 你在做什么?

248
00:18:02,782 --> 00:18:04,552
What? What you want me to.
啊? 不是你要我做的嘛

249
00:18:04,585 --> 00:18:07,398
But just for argument sake, what are you doing?
不过 保险起见问一句 你在做什么?

250
00:18:07,649 --> 00:18:09,794
I am trying to escape.
我想逃出去

251
00:18:09,882 --> 00:18:11,898
Oh... ya... escape,
哦... 对... 逃出去

252
00:18:11,902 --> 00:18:14,193
that's where I was going with that thing I just did.
我刚才就是想逃出去来着

253
00:18:14,197 --> 00:18:15,386
Wait, wait, wait, wait.
等等 等等 等等 等等

254
00:18:15,430 --> 00:18:17,680
Did you actually think we were gonna kiss?
你是不是真以为我会跟你接吻?

255
00:18:17,724 --> 00:18:19,432
- No, no, no, no, no !  - We just met!
- 没没没没没!  - 我们才刚刚见面!

256
00:18:19,684 --> 00:18:22,831
- Oh, mine!  - I think they need a little help.
- 哦 天呐!  - 我觉得它们需要点帮助

257
00:18:22,958 --> 00:18:25,855
I mean I know how my feathers look, but I'm not that kind of bird.
我是说 我知道我很帅 但我可不是花花公子

258
00:18:26,441 --> 00:18:28,128
# Say you say me #
# 说你 说我 #

259
00:18:28,194 --> 00:18:30,673
Okay, I had nothing to do with that.
好吧 这出可不是我整的

260
00:18:31,134 --> 00:18:34,177
But, it's actually a pretty good song.
不过 这首歌真是不错啊

261
00:18:35,765 --> 00:18:37,681
# Naturally... # 
# 情不自禁... #

262
00:18:37,683 --> 00:18:38,807
Yes, sing it Lionel.
对啦 唱吧 莱昂内尔(歌曲原唱)

263
00:18:43,981 --> 00:18:46,283
Wow, that was fast.
哇哦 发展够迅速的

264
00:18:46,922 --> 00:18:49,735
Lionel Richie. Works every time.
莱昂内尔・里奇的歌 屡试不爽

265
00:18:50,322 --> 00:18:52,947
We should probably give them some privacy.
咱们还是给它们留点私人空间吧

266
00:18:58,873 --> 00:19:02,207
I'm not so sure I should leave Blu here alone.
我不太放心把布鲁自己留在这

267
00:19:02,231 --> 00:19:03,741
Oh no, no, no, don't worry.
哦 没事 没事 没事 不用担心

268
00:19:03,752 --> 00:19:06,293
Sylvio will keep an eye on them all night.
索维欧会整晚盯着它们的

269
00:19:10,490 --> 00:19:12,635
Besides, he's got Jewel.
再说 他已经有珠儿了

270
00:19:19,561 --> 00:19:20,956
Help me!
救命!

271
00:19:25,610 --> 00:19:29,800
This is the final countdown to Carnival! Let's Samba.
现在是狂欢节最后一次倒计时! 一起跳桑巴吧

272
00:19:59,292 --> 00:20:02,606
Come here, poor little birdie.
过来吧 可怜的小鸟乖乖

273
00:20:03,004 --> 00:20:06,860
It's okay. I got you. I got you.
没事的 有我呢 有我呢

274
00:20:30,347 --> 00:20:31,763
Excuse me!
不好意思!

275
00:20:31,952 --> 00:20:34,744
Please, I'm trying to sleep.
拜托 我想睡觉啊

276
00:20:34,872 --> 00:20:39,041
I'm sorry, sleepy head, I'm trying to escape.
对不起哦 瞌睡虫 我想逃跑呢

277
00:20:40,502 --> 00:20:43,127
Escape, why? This cage is awesome.
逃跑 为什么啊? 这笼子多棒啊

278
00:20:43,172 --> 00:20:46,548
This cage...? Oh, what was I thinking?
这笼子...? 哦 我想什么呢?

279
00:20:46,885 --> 00:20:50,011
I wouldn't expect a pet to understand.
我可不指望一只宠物理解我

280
00:20:50,264 --> 00:20:52,555
Pet? Did you just call me a pet?
宠物? 你刚才叫我宠物?

281
00:20:52,642 --> 00:20:54,683
For the record, I am not a pet.
声明一下 我不是宠物

282
00:20:54,831 --> 00:20:56,059
I am a companion.
我是人类的伙伴

283
00:20:56,353 --> 00:20:57,727
And you know what? Do what you want.
还有 告诉你 随便你

284
00:20:57,732 --> 00:20:59,711
Cause' tomorrow morning Linda will come for me,
因为明天一早琳达就会来接我

285
00:20:59,713 --> 00:21:01,544
and this whole nightmare will be over.
这场噩梦就会彻底结束了

286
00:21:01,713 --> 00:21:05,091
Incredible, you'd rather be with a... a human
真不可思议 你宁愿跟... 跟人类在一起

287
00:21:05,096 --> 00:21:06,554
than with your own kind.
也不愿跟自己的同类相处

288
00:21:06,594 --> 00:21:10,659
Well, that human has given me love and affection for the past 15 years,
嗯 那个人类这15年来一直给我爱心和关怀

289
00:21:10,671 --> 00:21:13,797
whereas my own kind tries to strangle me after 15 seconds.
而我的同类见到我15秒之后就想掐死我

290
00:21:13,810 --> 00:21:16,720
Yah, it's because of them, I've lost everything.
对 正是因为他们 我才失去了一切

291
00:21:16,829 --> 00:21:18,287
You can't trust them!
你不能信任他们!

292
00:21:18,712 --> 00:21:21,024
Of course, you can trust humans.
你当然可以信任人类

293
00:21:22,548 --> 00:21:23,609
Jewel?
珠儿?

294
00:21:23,863 --> 00:21:24,924
Jewel?
珠儿?

295
00:21:25,968 --> 00:21:27,009
Hi, there!
你好啊!

296
00:21:37,294 --> 00:21:39,460
It's nice of you to join me for dinner.
很高兴能和你共进晚餐

297
00:21:39,608 --> 00:21:41,003
I often eat alone.
我通常都是一个人进餐

298
00:21:41,444 --> 00:21:43,798
Because of course my work.
当然 是我这份工作的原因

299
00:21:44,447 --> 00:21:47,156
I thought I was the "bird-mad" until I met you.
在认识你之前 我以为我才是"鸟痴"

300
00:21:47,179 --> 00:21:50,284
Yes, right. Do you have a favorite bird?
嗯 对啊 你有没有最喜欢的鸟?

301
00:21:50,308 --> 00:21:53,642
Well, obviously I'm a Blue Macaw kind of gal.
嗯 很显然我是蓝色金刚鹦鹉铁杆粉丝

302
00:21:54,145 --> 00:21:57,125
That makes sense. They are very handsome birds.
顺理成章啊 它们确实很漂亮

303
00:21:57,129 --> 00:21:59,607
Actually, it's the brains I'm attracted to.
其实 吸引我的是它们的智力

304
00:21:59,735 --> 00:22:02,235
I'm not so impressed by fancy feathers.
我对华丽的羽毛不是很感兴趣

305
00:22:02,405 --> 00:22:04,342
I know exactly what you mean.
我完全明白你的意思

306
00:22:04,427 --> 00:22:06,322
My favorite bird is the spotted owl.
我最喜欢的鸟是斑点猫头鹰

307
00:22:06,345 --> 00:22:10,020
I've always been mesmerized by those big,
我一直为那圆圆的 大而智慧的眼睛

308
00:22:10,026 --> 00:22:12,839
round intelligent eyes.
而着迷不已

309
00:22:16,064 --> 00:22:17,396
Chicken rolls?
鸡肉卷?

310
00:22:17,401 --> 00:22:18,754
Lambada.
跳个兰巴达舞

311
00:22:19,714 --> 00:22:21,192
Oh, chicken eyes.
哦 变成鸡的眼睛了

312
00:22:21,718 --> 00:22:22,863
Oh, Gosh!
哦 天!

313
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,729
Hello.
喂

314
00:22:53,251 --> 00:22:54,625
Oh, Blu.
哦 布鲁

315
00:22:55,483 --> 00:22:58,526
We should have never left Blu's cage.
我们就不该离开布鲁的笼子

316
00:22:59,048 --> 00:23:03,363
- This is all my fault.  - No, Linda, please.
- 都是我的错  - 不 琳达 别这样

317
00:23:03,409 --> 00:23:05,346
This is not your fault.
这不是你的错

318
00:23:06,745 --> 00:23:10,434
You're right, it's not my fault.
你说得对 不是我的错

319
00:23:10,790 --> 00:23:12,237
- It's your fault!  - What?
- 是你的错!  - 什么?

320
00:23:12,271 --> 00:23:14,229
With your little bird talk,
你用你的花言鸟语

321
00:23:14,232 --> 00:23:15,690
and that whole...
还有你那个...

322
00:23:17,111 --> 00:23:18,350
Well, you know what?
哼 告诉你吧?

323
00:23:18,353 --> 00:23:20,540
Squawk squawking is squawk-squawk!
就是你叽里呱啦 到处抗议抱怨!

324
00:23:21,301 --> 00:23:23,217
I am sorry. I didn't mean to curse.
对不起 我没想诅咒你

325
00:23:23,262 --> 00:23:25,068
I don't understand!
我想不通!

326
00:23:25,071 --> 00:23:27,242
Sylvio is the best guard in the business.
索维欧是业内最好的守卫了

327
00:23:27,267 --> 00:23:28,579
So let me get this straight.
让我先搞清楚经过

328
00:23:28,622 --> 00:23:30,705
You were attacked by a little white bird.
你被一只白色的小鸟袭击了

329
00:23:30,792 --> 00:23:35,170
Yes, with this rag he held it to my mouth, like this.
没错 他就这么抓着这块布堵住我嘴巴 像这样

330
00:23:42,970 --> 00:23:44,407
We're doomed.
我们完蛋了

331
00:23:51,709 --> 00:23:55,314
Okay, there's no place like home, there's no place like home.
好吧 这一点也不像家 一点也不像

332
00:23:55,567 --> 00:23:57,441
How I wish I was back in my cage
我真想回到自己的笼子啊

333
00:23:57,457 --> 00:24:00,489
with my mirror and my swing and my little bell.
那里有我的镜子 秋千还有小铃铛

334
00:24:00,866 --> 00:24:04,096
- How I miss my little bell.  - Ssshh, play dead.
- 真怀念我的小铃铛  - 嘘 装死

335
00:24:04,933 --> 00:24:07,809
What? I don't need to play dead. I'm about to have a heart attack.
什么? 我不需要装 我都快突发心脏病了

336
00:24:07,831 --> 00:24:10,540
- Just do it!  - Fine.
- 照做就是了!  - 好吧

337
00:24:16,570 --> 00:24:20,280
- Stop twitching.  - Come on, it's the twitching that sells it.
- 别抽了  - 拜托 有抽搐才逼真

338
00:24:24,391 --> 00:24:25,890
Come on in, Kid.
进来吧 小子

339
00:24:33,442 --> 00:24:37,152
Well, what do you know? Good work, Fernando.
嗯 知道吗? 干得不错 费尔南多

340
00:24:37,926 --> 00:24:41,845
You see, boys. What did I tell you about this one?
看到没 小的们 我上次是怎么说的?

341
00:24:42,390 --> 00:24:44,598
That you are going to pay him half as much as what you said?
说你打算只付说好价钱的一半?

342
00:24:44,663 --> 00:24:46,121
No, you idiot.
错 你个白痴

343
00:24:46,341 --> 00:24:49,144
That he reminds me of myself when I was that age.
我说 他让我想起我像他这么大的时候

344
00:24:49,354 --> 00:24:53,190
Smart, resourceful. Here you go, Kid.
聪明 又足智多谋 拿去吧 小子

345
00:24:54,362 --> 00:24:56,987
Hey, this is only half of what you promised me.
嘿 这还真是你答应给的一半啊

346
00:24:57,103 --> 00:24:58,363
Ah, shut up, Kid.
啊 闭嘴 小子

347
00:24:58,928 --> 00:25:00,302
What the...?
怎么...?

348
00:25:01,681 --> 00:25:05,102
I thought I told you I needed these birds alive.
我记得我说过这些鸟要活的

349
00:25:05,394 --> 00:25:08,478
Tell me, Fernando. Does this look alive to you?
告诉我 费尔南多 这看起来像是活的吗?

350
00:25:08,876 --> 00:25:10,000
Huh?
嗯?

351
00:25:11,650 --> 00:25:13,108
- Get it!  - Over here!
- 抓住它!  - 在那!

352
00:25:14,403 --> 00:25:15,610
Jewel!
珠儿!

353
00:25:24,831 --> 00:25:27,816
Hello, pretty bird.
你好啊 漂亮的小鸟

354
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:29,693
What's the matter?
怎么了?

355
00:25:29,697 --> 00:25:31,155
Cockatoo got your throat?
美冠鹦鹉掐到你喉咙了?

356
00:25:31,193 --> 00:25:34,122
Nigel, alive.
奈杰 要活的

357
00:25:34,926 --> 00:25:36,592
To be continued.
还没完哦

358
00:25:41,766 --> 00:25:44,600
That was your plan! To take off and leave me!
这就是你的计划! 扔下我自己飞走!

359
00:25:44,666 --> 00:25:45,853
Gee, thanks.
天 谢谢你

360
00:25:45,896 --> 00:25:47,916
Why didn't you follow me?
你为什么不跟着我?

361
00:25:49,942 --> 00:25:53,256
- Nice work, Nigel.  - Yah, nice work, Nigel.
- 干得漂亮 奈杰  - 是啊 干得漂亮 奈杰

362
00:25:54,091 --> 00:25:55,986
The last two Macawsan birds.
最后两只金刚鹦鹉

363
00:25:56,907 --> 00:25:58,740
These are worth a fortune.
这可值不少钱呢

364
00:25:58,785 --> 00:26:01,640
Hey, Fernando! Hang these up in the other room.
嘿 费尔南多! 把这个挂到隔壁去

365
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:18,679
Hey, birdie. Let me out! Let me out!
嘿 鸟儿 放我出去! 放我出去!

366
00:26:18,787 --> 00:26:19,868
Let me out of here!
让我离开这!

367
00:26:19,871 --> 00:26:23,225
Pretty bird. I'm a pretty bird. Pretty bird. I'm a pretty bird, hahaha!
漂漂鸟 我是一只漂漂鸟 漂漂鸟 我是一只漂漂鸟 哈哈哈!

368
00:26:23,477 --> 00:26:26,029
I was framed. They got the wrong guy.
我是被冤枉的 他们抓错人了

369
00:26:26,189 --> 00:26:28,730
Sorry guys. Nothing personal.
抱歉了伙计 我也不想的

370
00:26:39,371 --> 00:26:41,079
So, what is going to happen to them?
那么 它们接下来会怎样?

371
00:26:41,122 --> 00:26:44,623
Don't worry. We're going to find good homes for them.
别担心 我们会给他们找到合适的家的

372
00:26:45,418 --> 00:26:46,646
Now go home to Mama.
现在回家找妈妈去吧

373
00:26:46,659 --> 00:26:49,002
- But I don't have a Mama.  - Father?
- 但是我没有妈妈  - 父亲?

374
00:26:49,088 --> 00:26:51,004
- Brother?  - Gold fish?
- 兄弟?  - 金鱼?

375
00:26:51,718 --> 00:26:53,509
Can we keep him, Boss?
咱能把他留这吗 老大?

376
00:26:54,991 --> 00:26:56,073
No!
不行!

377
00:26:57,202 --> 00:27:00,057
So Marcel, what's really going to happen to those birds?
那 马塞尔 那些鸟究竟会怎样?

378
00:27:00,101 --> 00:27:02,642
Dulled, plucked, stuffed, eaten, who cares.
打晕 拔毛 喂肥 吃掉 管他呢

379
00:27:02,729 --> 00:27:05,083
All I know is, we are going to be rich.
我只知道 咱们要发财了

380
00:27:06,483 --> 00:27:08,587
We're gonna to be rich.
咱们要发财了

381
00:27:56,203 --> 00:27:58,223
Come on, come on, the game's starting.
快来 快来 比赛要开始了

382
00:27:58,446 --> 00:28:01,645
Yes, you be very clear. Tomorrow or the deal is off.
是 你说得很清楚了 明天交货 否则免谈

383
00:28:02,168 --> 00:28:04,397
Of course, I have both the Macaws.
当然 两只金刚鹦鹉我都抓到了

384
00:28:04,587 --> 00:28:06,649
Yes, I'll deliver them myself.
对 我会亲自把它们运过去

385
00:28:06,863 --> 00:28:08,318
Au revoir.
再见

386
00:28:09,508 --> 00:28:12,259
Alright you two, we load the truck tonight.
好了 你俩听着 我们今晚装车

387
00:28:12,388 --> 00:28:15,264
First thing in the morning, we bring those birds to the airport.
明早第一件事就是带鸟儿们去机场

388
00:28:15,933 --> 00:28:16,473
You got it? 
明白没?

389
00:28:16,558 --> 00:28:18,141
- Yeah, sure, yeah.  - Heard you.
- 嗯 是 是  - 听到啦

390
00:28:18,332 --> 00:28:21,104
And one of you, feed Nigel.
还有 你俩其中一个 来喂奈杰

391
00:28:27,758 --> 00:28:29,882
Rock paper scissors, shoot.
剪刀 石头 布

392
00:28:30,011 --> 00:28:33,376
- Yes!  - No... no, scissors cut rock.
- 耶!  - 不... 不对 剪刀剪掉石头

393
00:28:33,379 --> 00:28:35,670
Oh, man, how come you always win?
不是吧 怎么每次都是你赢?

394
00:28:39,521 --> 00:28:41,229
Nice birdie.
可爱的小鸟

395
00:28:45,027 --> 00:28:46,485
Here you go.
拿去吧

396
00:28:54,704 --> 00:28:56,245
Ughh, cannibal.
呃 食人族

397
00:28:57,624 --> 00:29:00,750
Okay, hold it together. The key is not to panic.
好吧 要淡定 关键是别慌

398
00:29:00,763 --> 00:29:01,819
I'm not panicking.
我没慌

399
00:29:01,826 --> 00:29:03,940
I wasn't talking to you. I was talking to me.
我没跟你说话 我自言自语来着

400
00:29:03,963 --> 00:29:06,839
But it's okay. Any minute now, Linda will find us.
不过没关系 现在起 琳达随时会找到我们

401
00:29:06,883 --> 00:29:10,327
Oh, great, and then she'll just stick us behind another set of bars, right?
哦 太好了 然后她会把我们装进另一个囚牢里是吧?

402
00:29:10,331 --> 00:29:11,715
Yes, I mean no!
对 我是说 不对!

403
00:29:11,723 --> 00:29:15,955
Look, pet cages might work for you but I don't want to belong to anyone.
听着 宠物笼可能对你胃口 但我不想属于任何人

404
00:29:24,048 --> 00:29:27,466
Something seems to be lodged in my beak.
好像有什么卡在我的嘴里了

405
00:29:27,510 --> 00:29:29,572
Would you mind?
帮个忙呗?

406
00:29:43,361 --> 00:29:45,976
Oh, I know I'm not a pretty birdie.
哦 我知道我不是漂漂的小鸟

407
00:29:45,981 --> 00:29:48,855
But I used to be quite a looker.
不过我也曾经帅过

408
00:29:48,908 --> 00:29:50,386
The star.
巨星

409
00:29:52,370 --> 00:29:55,392
Lights, camera, action.
灯光 摄像 开始

410
00:29:55,436 --> 00:29:57,706
# I was striking svelte. #
# 曾经的我 骨感如你 #

411
00:29:57,730 --> 00:29:59,959
# Ambitious feet-to-beak. #
# 从头到脚 雄心壮志 #

412
00:29:59,972 --> 00:30:01,263
# So birdie-licious. #
# 如此这般 鸟色可餐 #

413
00:30:01,276 --> 00:30:04,157
# Now I'm vile. I'm villain and vicious. #
# 事到如今 我已跌堕 #

414
00:30:04,173 --> 00:30:05,900
# Oh, and malicious. #
# 对了还有 作恶多端 #

415
00:30:05,906 --> 00:30:08,572
# I had it all, TV shows, women too.#
# 我曾拥有 名声女色 #

416
00:30:08,617 --> 00:30:11,326
# I was tall. Over 1 foot 2. #
# 雄姿挺拔 过一尺二 #

417
00:30:11,348 --> 00:30:13,910
# Then they got a pretty parrot to fill my shoes. #
# 可谁曾想 靓仔接班 #

418
00:30:13,936 --> 00:30:16,186
# That's why I am so evil, why I do what I do. #
# 就因如是 我才至此 #

419
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:18,991
# - He was a superstar.  - So young and vital. #
# - 他是明星  - 年轻有型 #

420
00:30:19,013 --> 00:30:21,461
# - He's nasty.  - A Southern American idol. #
# - 今变恶棍  - 南美偶像 #

421
00:30:21,485 --> 00:30:24,047
# - He's a vicious bird.  - Who said that about me? #
# - 是只恶鸟  - 谁说我呢? #

422
00:30:24,072 --> 00:30:26,760
# - A very vicious bird.  - I'll have you rotisseried. #
# - 超大恶鸟  - 我来你烤你 #

423
00:30:26,783 --> 00:30:29,841
# I am a feathery freak with beak, a bird murderer. #
# 喙利羽丰 鸟类杀手 #

424
00:30:29,865 --> 00:30:32,557
# You think you're better than me. I've never heard of you. #
# 你比我强 从未听说 #

425
00:30:32,581 --> 00:30:35,164
# I'm evil. I'll feed your cheese balls with weevils. #
# 我是恶魔 喂你奶酪 #

426
00:30:35,187 --> 00:30:38,355
# I poop on people and I blame it on seagulls. #
# 播撒便便 嫁祸海鸥 #

427
00:30:38,503 --> 00:30:39,705
# It was him. #
# 是他是他 #

428
00:30:39,714 --> 00:30:42,130
# - He's a nasty bird  - I'm invincible. #
# - 这只恶鸟  - 天下无敌 #

429
00:30:42,216 --> 00:30:43,463
# He's ghastly. #
# 恐怖阴森 #

430
00:30:43,468 --> 00:30:47,479
# I'm invincible, I'm unwashable, unrinsible. #
# 天下无敌 不擦不洗 #

431
00:30:47,482 --> 00:30:49,920
# Like an abandoned school, I have no principles. #
# 有如废校 没有原则 #

432
00:30:49,924 --> 00:30:52,226
# All of you Brazilian birds #
# 巴西鸟儿 #

433
00:30:52,437 --> 00:30:54,749
# All 18 million birds. #
# 1800万只鸟 #

434
00:30:54,772 --> 00:30:57,275
# I'll tell you what I'm going to do. #
# 我要怎做 你来听好 #

435
00:30:57,278 --> 00:30:59,971
# I'm going to make you... #
# 要让你们... #

436
00:31:00,298 --> 00:31:02,026
Shut up now, shut up!
闭嘴 都给我闭嘴!

437
00:31:03,154 --> 00:31:04,320
Just me.
我独唱

438
00:31:04,573 --> 00:31:10,243
# I will make you ugly too. #
# 要让你们 也变丑陋 #

439
00:31:10,622 --> 00:31:13,017
- Hey!  - Sweet nightmares.
- 嘿!  - 甜蜜的噩梦

440
00:31:15,377 --> 00:31:18,836
Not cool, man. Scary, but not cool!
一点都不帅 伙计 很吓人 但不帅!

441
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:21,289
- Hey, are you okay?  - No.
- 嘿 你还好吧?  - 不

442
00:31:21,300 --> 00:31:23,591
I'm definitely not okay!
我一点都不好!

443
00:31:23,635 --> 00:31:26,010
- What... wait, wait! What are you doing?  - Getting out of here.
- 你... 等等 等等! 你在做什么?  - 逃跑啊

444
00:31:26,264 --> 00:31:27,841
You going to help me, or what?
你要来帮忙吗 还是怎样?

445
00:31:27,849 --> 00:31:31,726
Actually our survival guide said to sit and wait, and... and help will come.
事实上 求生手册上是这么说的 静坐着等待 然后... 然后救援就会来

446
00:31:31,769 --> 00:31:33,221
No one is coming!
没人会来!

447
00:31:33,230 --> 00:31:37,253
We are on our own and if we just sit here, we're going to die!
我们只有靠自己 如果静坐 只能等死!

448
00:31:38,652 --> 00:31:41,570
Yes, yes, yes.
好球 好球 好球

449
00:31:41,989 --> 00:31:43,030
No!
不!

450
00:31:43,282 --> 00:31:45,323
Nigel, get out of the way!
奈杰 别挡着我们看球!

451
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:50,912
Stop, stop. Why don't you just open the door?
停下 停下 直接开门不就好了吗?

452
00:31:51,707 --> 00:31:55,125
- Are you kidding me?  - Why? It's just a standard flip slide ball. Just...
- 你在耍我吗?  - 怎么? 这只是个普通的门闩而已 只要...

453
00:31:56,504 --> 00:31:57,545
What are you doing?
你在做什么?

454
00:31:57,631 --> 00:31:59,797
- Well, I can't...  - What? You can't what?
- 呃 我不会...  - 什么? 你不会什么?

455
00:32:04,305 --> 00:32:07,348
I can't fly!
我不会飞!

456
00:32:07,892 --> 00:32:11,936
- You couldn't tell me before now!  - It didn't matter before now.
- 你就不能早点告诉我吗!  - 之前没这必要啊

457
00:32:15,568 --> 00:32:16,984
I hate you.
我恨你

458
00:32:19,988 --> 00:32:21,821
- Is there anything else I need to know?  - Yes!
- 还有什么是我该知道的吗?  - 听着!

459
00:32:21,865 --> 00:32:24,115
I can't fly, I pick my beak and once in a while I pee in the bird bath.
我不会飞 我会挖鼻屎 时不时我还会在洗澡时尿尿

460
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,743
Happy?
满意没?

461
00:32:25,911 --> 00:32:27,744
- There they are!  - We got to get out of here!
- 他们在那儿!  - 我们得赶快离开这儿!

462
00:32:31,667 --> 00:32:33,036
Wait, wait. Listen to me.
等等 等等 听我说

463
00:32:33,044 --> 00:32:35,622
Flying may not be my thing, but walking is. Follow my lead.
或许飞行不是我的特长 但是步行我拿手 跟着我的口令

464
00:32:35,631 --> 00:32:37,797
- Inside right, outside left.  - Okay, I've got it.
- 左脚前 右脚后  - 好 我明白了

465
00:32:37,965 --> 00:32:40,340
Inside, outside, inside, outside...
左 右 左 右...

466
00:32:44,431 --> 00:32:45,805
- Yes, yes!  - Come on!
- 好球 好球!  - 来吧!

467
00:32:55,235 --> 00:32:57,359
See, I'm bilingual too.
看见没 我还精通外语

468
00:33:01,784 --> 00:33:03,021
Ah, this is great!
啊 这多棒啊!

469
00:33:03,024 --> 00:33:05,320
I'm chained to the only bird in the world who can't fly!
我和世界上唯一不会飞的那只鸟锁一块儿了!

470
00:33:05,329 --> 00:33:07,766
Actually, there are 40 species of flightless birds.
事实上 世界上有40种不会飞的鸟类

471
00:33:07,771 --> 00:33:09,082
- Duck!  - No, Ducks can fly!
- 低头!(鸭子!)  - 不对哦 鸭子会飞!

472
00:33:09,126 --> 00:33:10,917
No! Duck!
不! 我叫你低头!

473
00:33:19,552 --> 00:33:20,718
Yeah!
耶!

474
00:33:31,690 --> 00:33:32,751
Yes!
好球!

475
00:33:43,182 --> 00:33:44,223
Yes!
很好!

476
00:33:44,226 --> 00:33:45,267
Calm down!
小心!

477
00:33:48,293 --> 00:33:51,586
Nooo! Nooorrr!
不! 不不不不不!

478
00:34:01,807 --> 00:34:04,328
Get out of here, you putrid poultry.
滚开 你们这些破家禽

479
00:34:22,413 --> 00:34:24,246
- Oh, what was that?  - A stick.
- 哦 那是什么?  - 一根棍子

480
00:34:24,539 --> 00:34:27,205
- Ahh, and that?  - It's just a rock.
- 啊 那个呢?  - 一块石头而已

481
00:34:30,693 --> 00:34:33,564
- Is that a spider on your back?  - Will you quit it?
- 我背上是不是有只蜘蛛?  - 你消停下行不?

482
00:34:33,884 --> 00:34:36,342
It's just a leaf. Turn around.
只是片树叶 转过来

483
00:34:40,806 --> 00:34:41,847
Leaf.
树叶来着

484
00:34:41,892 --> 00:34:43,079
Told you.
都跟你说了

485
00:34:44,144 --> 00:34:46,391
Just come on, we need to find a safe place to spend the night.
来吧 我们得找个安全的地方过夜

486
00:34:46,397 --> 00:34:48,980
Safe? Safe! We're in the jungle!
安全? 安全! 我们在丛林里!

487
00:34:49,089 --> 00:34:51,003
You know when people say it's a jungle out there,
你知道通常人们提到丛林

488
00:34:51,026 --> 00:34:53,130
I'm pretty sure they don't mean it as a good thing.
我保证都不是什么好事

489
00:34:53,164 --> 00:34:57,073
Look, I hate to break it to you but this is where our kind naturally lives.
听着 很抱歉告诉你实话 但这里才是我们种族自然生活的地方

490
00:34:57,159 --> 00:35:00,618
Hey, hey, don't talk to me about nature. I watch Animal Planet.
嘿 嘿 别拿自然忽悠我 我可有看动物星球频道

491
00:35:00,662 --> 00:35:02,703
I know all about the food chain.
我了解所有的食物链

492
00:35:05,897 --> 00:35:08,413
You see, you see, out here I'm just a hors d'oeuvre.
看见没 看见没 在这儿我就是碟开胃菜

493
00:35:08,522 --> 00:35:10,709
Nothing more than a feathery spring roll.
顶多算一盘带羽毛的春卷

494
00:35:10,735 --> 00:35:13,861
That is why we stay on the trees and not on the ground.
这就是为什么我们要呆在树上 而不是地上

495
00:35:14,010 --> 00:35:15,342
After you.
你先上

496
00:35:16,430 --> 00:35:18,117
Oh, no, I don't think so.
哦 不 我不这么想

497
00:35:18,868 --> 00:35:22,119
I'll feel much more comfortable in something man-made.
还是给我个人造小屋什么的 我更有安全感

498
00:35:24,334 --> 00:35:25,896
Hey, how about up there?
嘿 那上面怎么样?

499
00:35:28,671 --> 00:35:32,214
I can't believe I've to drag your clumsy butt up there.
真不敢相信 我得拖着你愚蠢的大屁股上去

500
00:35:32,675 --> 00:35:35,216
Drag me? Watch and learn.
拖着我? 看好学着点

501
00:35:38,182 --> 00:35:40,098
Oh, Blu! Oh, just wait!
哦 布鲁! 哦 等等啊!

502
00:35:40,580 --> 00:35:41,141
Blu!
布鲁!

503
00:35:42,207 --> 00:35:44,253
Who's dragging whose butt now, huh?
现在是谁拖着谁的大屁股呢 哈?

504
00:35:44,256 --> 00:35:46,443
Ha, ha, very funny.
哈哈 很幽默

505
00:35:54,095 --> 00:35:55,678
You see, who needs flying?
看到没 谁要会飞啊?

506
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:58,389
Birds, birds need flying.
鸟啊 鸟类要会飞

507
00:35:58,537 --> 00:36:01,645
Flying is... is freedom
飞行意味着... 意味着自由

508
00:36:01,649 --> 00:36:04,508
and not having to rely on anyone.
不用依赖别人

509
00:36:05,441 --> 00:36:07,211
Don't you want that?
你难道不想吗?

510
00:36:07,568 --> 00:36:09,818
I don't know. Sounds a little lonely.
我不知道 听起来有点寂寞

511
00:36:11,655 --> 00:36:13,425
Let's get some sleep.
睡会儿吧

512
00:36:14,449 --> 00:36:16,990
I'm probably going to be up for a little while.
我可能暂时先不睡

513
00:36:17,078 --> 00:36:19,492
Because I'm still on Minnesota's time.
因为我生物钟还在明尼苏达州呢

514
00:36:19,705 --> 00:36:21,121
Good night.
晚安

515
00:36:22,125 --> 00:36:23,624
Good night, Jewel.
晚安 珠儿

516
00:36:27,004 --> 00:36:28,503
Good night, Linda.
晚安 琳达

517
00:36:35,826 --> 00:36:39,265
Excuse me, sir. Have you seen my bird?
打扰了 先生 你见过我的鸟吗?

518
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:42,248
Have... have you seen my bird?
你... 你见过我的鸟吗?

519
00:36:45,087 --> 00:36:48,526
Excuse me, uh, have you seen my bird?
不好意思 呃 请问你见过我的鸟吗?

520
00:37:08,465 --> 00:37:11,966
寻鸟启事 失踪的鸟--布鲁

521
00:37:23,588 --> 00:37:25,316
Have you seen my bird?
你见过我的鸟吗?

522
00:37:27,216 --> 00:37:29,174
Lady, American lady.
小姐 美国来的小姐

523
00:37:29,509 --> 00:37:31,092
Blu? Blu?
布鲁? 布鲁?

524
00:37:32,325 --> 00:37:33,178
Oh.
哦

525
00:37:34,932 --> 00:37:35,785
Wow.
哇

526
00:37:36,143 --> 00:37:39,561
- I know where your birds are.  - You found Blu? Are you sure?
- 我知道你的鸟在哪儿  - 你找到布鲁了? 你确定?

527
00:37:40,605 --> 00:37:41,646
It's his.
这是他的

528
00:37:41,649 --> 00:37:42,783
Let me see that.
让我看看

529
00:37:49,011 --> 00:37:50,072
You're right.
没错

530
00:37:50,116 --> 00:37:51,844
Okay, where is he?
好吧 他在哪儿?

531
00:37:51,889 --> 00:37:54,139
Come on, let's go. I'll take you to him.
来吧 我们走 我带你去找他

532
00:37:54,475 --> 00:37:57,538
No, no, no, Linda, wait. We don't know this boy.
不 不 不 琳达 等等 我们不认识这孩子

533
00:37:57,604 --> 00:37:59,020
We can't trust him.
我们不能相信他

534
00:38:02,213 --> 00:38:04,594
I have to trust him.
我必须得相信他

535
00:38:05,015 --> 00:38:06,994
I don't have a choice.
我没得选

536
00:38:20,253 --> 00:38:22,857
Do you think I'm an idiot?
你们把我当白痴吗?

537
00:38:23,986 --> 00:38:28,408
There were two birds, chained together, in a cage.
他们是两只鸟 不仅锁在一起 还被关在笼子里

538
00:38:28,417 --> 00:38:29,885
How could you lose them?
这样你们都能把他们弄丢?

539
00:38:29,899 --> 00:38:32,837
They out smart us, boss. But don't worry.
老大 他们比我们还聪明 不过别担心

540
00:38:32,849 --> 00:38:35,474
We'll get them back. I have a plan.
我们会把它们抓回来的 我有个计划

541
00:38:35,488 --> 00:38:37,540
Oh, great. What are you going to do?
哦 很好 你准备怎么做?

542
00:38:37,563 --> 00:38:41,524
Wonder in the city, calling "Here birdie-birdie, here birdie!"
在城市里四处叫唤 "小鸟乖乖 乖乖小鸟!"

543
00:38:41,567 --> 00:38:44,526
Well, anything sounds dumb when you say it like that.
呃 照你这口气 不管什么方法听起来都很傻

544
00:38:46,072 --> 00:38:48,738
We have to get birds to the airport by tonight.
今晚之前 我们必须带着那些鸟到达机场

545
00:38:48,825 --> 00:38:51,743
But it's Carnival. All the roads will be blocked by the parade.
但今天是狂欢节 游行队伍会封死道路啊

546
00:38:51,787 --> 00:38:54,934
That's why I wanted to go this morning!
所以我本打算今早出发的!

547
00:38:55,081 --> 00:38:56,122
Nigel!
奈杰!

548
00:38:56,709 --> 00:39:00,356
This bird is ten times smarter than the two of you combined.
这只鸟比你们俩加在一块还要聪明十倍

549
00:39:00,921 --> 00:39:04,151
Yeah, well, if he's so smart, why don't you put him in charge?
是啊是啊 那如果他真这么聪明 你怎么不让他负责这事儿?

550
00:39:04,196 --> 00:39:06,258
I am putting him in charge.
我正打算让他负责

551
00:39:07,678 --> 00:39:09,490
Stop suggesting things!
别再提建议了!

552
00:39:09,828 --> 00:39:11,327
Go find them, Nigel.
去找到他们 奈杰

553
00:39:20,213 --> 00:39:23,381
Hmm, if we can't get through the parade,
嗯 如果我们无法穿过游行队伍

554
00:39:23,467 --> 00:39:25,341
we'll have to be in the parade.
干脆加入好了

555
00:39:25,365 --> 00:39:26,406
Huh?
哈?

556
00:39:30,182 --> 00:39:33,475
- Are you sure this is going to work?  - Positive.
- 你确定这管用吗?  - 必须的

557
00:39:33,728 --> 00:39:35,102
Check my map.
看我的分析图

558
00:39:35,813 --> 00:39:38,814
Yes, that's... that's just comforting. Thank you.
是啊 这... 这让我很欣慰 多谢

559
00:39:38,984 --> 00:39:41,400
Look, let's just get this chain broken.
听着 我们得把铁链解开

560
00:39:41,404 --> 00:39:43,899
Right, then we can go find Linda.
没错 然后我们就可以去找琳达了

561
00:39:43,904 --> 00:39:46,122
No, you can go find Linda.
不对 是你就可以去找琳达了

562
00:39:46,137 --> 00:39:49,325
Once this chain is off, I'm going back to being free in the jungle.
一旦这铁链解开了 我就会重返自由回到丛林的怀抱

563
00:39:49,369 --> 00:39:51,077
- Deal?  - Fine, deal.
- 一言为定?  - 好 一言为定

564
00:39:58,566 --> 00:40:00,503
Nice try, brainiac.
干得漂亮 聪明人

565
00:40:04,199 --> 00:40:05,924
Oh, I think something is watching us.
哦 我觉得有东西在盯着我们

566
00:40:11,290 --> 00:40:14,791
Oh, be careful, Blu. They might snuggle you to death.
哦 小心点 布鲁 他们会撒娇腻死你哦

567
00:40:16,379 --> 00:40:17,962
Oh, come here.
哦 过来

568
00:40:36,733 --> 00:40:38,316
Attack!
攻击!

569
00:40:41,133 --> 00:40:43,174
What is going on down there?
下面在闹什么呢?

570
00:40:44,325 --> 00:40:46,137
Go, go, go. Off with you.
走开 走开 走开 离开这儿

571
00:40:46,182 --> 00:40:48,995
Okay, guys, guys. I told you a thousand times.
好啦 孩子们 孩子们 跟你们说了上千次了

572
00:40:49,019 --> 00:40:52,353
Manuela, Sofia, Kamana, listen to me. Ow! O'yah, right in the eye.
曼纽尔 索非亚 卡马纳 听我说 嗷! 很好 戳到眼睛啦

573
00:40:52,458 --> 00:40:54,291
Oh, precious, ain't they?
哦 太可爱了 不是吗?

574
00:40:54,398 --> 00:40:57,190
The kids! Seventeen of them and one on the way.
我的孩子! 17个啦 还有个就快出生了

575
00:40:57,236 --> 00:41:00,445
Hey... you, stop that! Stop shaking them.
嘿... 你们 放下! 别晃他们

576
00:41:02,553 --> 00:41:04,721
They have given me great feathers.
拜他们所赐 我羽毛都不剩多少了

577
00:41:04,726 --> 00:41:07,226
Oh, this Papa needs a break.
哦 爸爸要休息会儿啦

578
00:41:07,371 --> 00:41:09,954
So, you two love birds headed for Carnival?
这么看来 你们小情侣是要去狂欢节?

579
00:41:10,125 --> 00:41:12,771
- Wow, love birds?  - We're more like acquaintance birds.
- 哇 情侣?  - 我们顶多算熟人

580
00:41:12,783 --> 00:41:15,560
And not even that. We're more like "chained-together" birds.
连熟人都算不上 我们更像是"被锁在一起" 仅此而已

581
00:41:15,567 --> 00:41:17,129
Yes, I mean... Ouch!
没错 我是说... 嗷!

582
00:41:17,694 --> 00:41:20,073
What is it with these kids and the feathers?
这些孩子怎么总跟羽毛过不去?

583
00:41:20,077 --> 00:41:22,353
We have no idea, we're having them tested.
我们也不知道 我们准备带他们去做检查

584
00:41:22,366 --> 00:41:27,431
So, do you think you could help us get this thing off?
那 你可以帮我们把这玩意儿弄下来吗?

585
00:41:28,373 --> 00:41:33,165
Lucky for you, you know Rafael, and Rafael knows everyone.
你们真幸运 你们认识了拉斐尔 而拉斐尔认识全世界

586
00:41:33,211 --> 00:41:34,700
Ow! Again in the eye!
嗷! 又戳到眼睛啦!

587
00:41:34,712 --> 00:41:36,114
Okay, you want me to call your mother!
好吧 你们是要我叫妈妈来啦!

588
00:41:36,118 --> 00:41:37,159
No!
不要!

589
00:41:37,174 --> 00:41:39,715
Works every time. They are scared to death of her.
很次都奏效 他们可害怕她了

590
00:41:39,730 --> 00:41:41,323
Call me for what?
叫我来干什么?

591
00:41:41,678 --> 00:41:43,198
Eva, my love.
伊娃 亲爱的

592
00:41:43,452 --> 00:41:45,573
I must take this young couple to see Luiz.
我要带这对小情侣去见路易兹

593
00:41:45,576 --> 00:41:46,658
Luiz?
路易兹?

594
00:41:46,788 --> 00:41:49,329
You don't fool me for a second.
你可骗不了我

595
00:41:49,394 --> 00:41:52,437
You and your amigos just want to sneak off to Carnival.
你和你的朋友只是想偷偷溜去狂欢节吧

596
00:41:53,150 --> 00:41:54,701
Oh, Carnival.
哦 狂欢节

597
00:41:54,705 --> 00:41:59,029
That magical time when I met the most beautiful bird in the world.
在那神奇的时刻 我遇见了世界上最美的小鸟

598
00:42:01,533 --> 00:42:06,109
I still remember the song that was playing when I first laid eyes on you.
我还记得我第一次见你时 放的那首歌

599
00:42:06,331 --> 00:42:09,991
# Tall and tanning, young and lovely, #
# 高挑身姿 古铜肌肤 年轻活力 可爱甜美 #

600
00:42:09,994 --> 00:42:13,858
# The girl from Ipanema goes walking. #
# 这来自伊帕内玛的女孩与我擦肩而过 #

601
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,129
Come on baby, sing it.
来吧 宝贝 唱起来

602
00:42:15,133 --> 00:42:16,486
# And when she passes #
# 当她走过我的身边 #

603
00:42:16,489 --> 00:42:20,126
# Each one she passes goes "Aah!!!" # 
# 每个人都情不自禁为她喝彩 "啊!!!" #

604
00:42:22,014 --> 00:42:24,493
Like a river of the sweetest honey.
像是世界最甜美的声音

605
00:42:25,248 --> 00:42:26,997
I guess love is deaf too.
我想爱情也是会让人失聪的

606
00:42:27,009 --> 00:42:28,050
Come here, mmm.
过来 Mua

607
00:42:31,649 --> 00:42:35,985
Okay, take them to Luiz, but hurry back.
好吧 带他们去找路易兹 但要早点回来哦

608
00:42:36,029 --> 00:42:37,653
You are an angel.
你就像个天使

609
00:42:37,781 --> 00:42:39,822
I'll miss you, my juicy little mango.
我会想你的 我鲜嫩多汁的小芒果

610
00:42:40,032 --> 00:42:42,469
Oh, me too. My pouchy papaya.
哦 我也是 我胖胖脸的小木瓜

611
00:42:43,536 --> 00:42:46,870
Hey! Paco, Carlos! Put your brother down, now!
嘿! 帕高 卡洛斯! 把你们的弟弟放下 立刻!

612
00:42:46,916 --> 00:42:48,873
I can't believe she actually let me go.
真不敢相信 她真的放我走了

613
00:42:48,877 --> 00:42:51,022
So how far is this Luiz?
那个路易兹那儿离这儿有多远?

614
00:42:51,025 --> 00:42:53,976
Not far, 30 minutes says the crow flies.
不远 直线飞过去30分钟吧

615
00:42:54,569 --> 00:42:56,548
And how long does the Macaw walks?
那金刚鹦鹉走过去要多久?

616
00:42:56,676 --> 00:42:58,516
Bobo here can't fly.
这小子不会飞

617
00:42:58,521 --> 00:43:00,395
- But he's a bird.  - Not all birds fly.
- 但他是只鸟啊  - 并不是所有的鸟都会飞

618
00:43:00,399 --> 00:43:02,508
- There are Ostriches...  - You're not an Ostrich.
- 鸵鸟就不会...  - 你又不是鸵鸟

619
00:43:02,515 --> 00:43:03,999
- Well, not technically.  - Wait, wait, wait...
- 呃 理论上说不是而已  - 等等 等等 等等...

620
00:43:04,013 --> 00:43:06,555
My friends, I want to help you, but to walk the whole way,
朋友们 我想帮你们 可是要全程步行

621
00:43:06,558 --> 00:43:08,336
- it...it can't be done!  - Where's daddy?
- 这... 这根本不可能!  - 爸爸在哪儿?

622
00:43:08,346 --> 00:43:10,856
Daddy, daddy!
爸爸 爸爸!

623
00:43:10,984 --> 00:43:13,002
But hey, we might as well give it a shot.
但 嘿 我们还是试一试吧

624
00:43:13,005 --> 00:43:14,068
Let's go, quickly.
出发吧 快快快

625
00:43:14,075 --> 00:43:16,319
No, no, no, don't look back. They sense fear.
不不不 别回头 他们感受得到恐惧

626
00:43:30,214 --> 00:43:32,026
注意 禁止喂野生动物

627
00:43:42,205 --> 00:43:44,329
What an adorable monkey.
多可爱的猴子啊

628
00:44:01,371 --> 00:44:03,099
Hey, my watch!
嘿 我的手表!

629
00:44:29,193 --> 00:44:30,499
Hello, boys.
孩子们 你们好啊

630
00:44:30,511 --> 00:44:33,001
Seems like you had a busy day.
看来你们这一天很忙碌啊

631
00:44:33,052 --> 00:44:34,317
Oh, what? This?
哦 怎么? 这个吗?

632
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:37,252
This is just some stuff we found.
这只是我们找到的一些东西

633
00:44:37,264 --> 00:44:39,009
Right, boys?
对吧 小的们?

634
00:44:39,528 --> 00:44:42,018
I'm not interested in your nicked knickknacks.
我对你们这些小勾当没兴趣

635
00:44:42,186 --> 00:44:44,916
Your burgle-bobbles bore me.
你们这样的盗窃方法可闷死我了

636
00:44:44,942 --> 00:44:47,419
There are two blue Macaws out there.
有两只蓝色的金刚鹦鹉不见了

637
00:44:47,755 --> 00:44:51,527
And I need your multitude of vice to help me find them.
我需要你和你手下的小喽来帮我找到他们

638
00:44:51,655 --> 00:44:54,510
Oh, yes, what's in it for us?
哦 是啊 那我们有什么好处?

639
00:44:55,012 --> 00:44:56,824
That's a fair question.
问得好

640
00:45:01,520 --> 00:45:03,123
Let's discuss it.
我们来商量商量

641
00:45:06,129 --> 00:45:07,981
I certainly see your point.
很显然 我明白你的意思

642
00:45:07,985 --> 00:45:10,726
But what could I possibly do for you in return?
但我能用什么来回报你呢?

643
00:45:11,071 --> 00:45:12,581
Save me, save me!
救我 救我!

644
00:45:12,589 --> 00:45:14,906
Oh, that's a thought.
哦 这想法不错啊

645
00:45:15,014 --> 00:45:16,367
This is enough?
就这样?

646
00:45:16,374 --> 00:45:18,588
I don't want to feel like I'm cheating you.
我可不想让你觉得我是在骗你

647
00:45:18,664 --> 00:45:19,236
Help me, help me, help me.
救我 救我 救我

648
00:45:19,289 --> 00:45:21,424
We'll do it, we'll do it. Save me, please.
我们会照办的 我们会照办的 求你 救我

649
00:45:21,895 --> 00:45:24,207
Save me!
救我!

650
00:45:26,421 --> 00:45:29,005
Alright, you twisted my wing. Deal.
好吧 我有出手救你 成交

651
00:45:29,769 --> 00:45:32,133
Now then, any more questions?
现在 还有问题吗?

652
00:45:32,814 --> 00:45:34,407
No? Good!
没了哈? 很好!

653
00:45:34,638 --> 00:45:38,452
You'll spread out and find these Macaws by the end of the day.
你们分头行动 天黑之前找到这两只金刚鹦鹉

654
00:45:38,456 --> 00:45:41,060
Or it's flying lessons for everyone!
不然 就让你们每人感受一下从天而降的乐趣!

655
00:45:41,065 --> 00:45:42,314
Go!
快去!

656
00:45:44,671 --> 00:45:47,076
Go do your monkey business.
做好你们的事

657
00:46:02,168 --> 00:46:03,855
I changed my mind.
我改主意了

658
00:46:04,733 --> 00:46:07,118
Maybe we can find a bus schedule or something.
不如我们去看看公车时刻表什么的吧

659
00:46:07,132 --> 00:46:09,329
Come on, you are not going to back out now?
不是吧你 你不会退缩了吧?

660
00:46:09,552 --> 00:46:11,510
Not in front of a lady.
在女士面前可不能退缩

661
00:46:13,326 --> 00:46:15,378
Okay, yes..., sure.
好吧 好... 好的

662
00:46:15,485 --> 00:46:17,202
All right, that's the spirit.
好了 就是要这样的态度

663
00:46:17,206 --> 00:46:18,798
You sure you're up for this?
你确定你要飞?

664
00:46:19,407 --> 00:46:20,937
Yeah, yeah, I mean it's not like 
当然 当然 我是说 

665
00:46:20,939 --> 00:46:23,171
we're hurdling ourselves off the mountain or something.
反正这又不是从高山上掉下来

666
00:46:23,755 --> 00:46:24,796
Right?
对吗?

667
00:46:24,798 --> 00:46:27,192
Actually that was pretty much my entire plan.
事实上 我就是这么计划的

668
00:46:27,248 --> 00:46:30,551
- What?  - Don't worry Blu. It's in your DNA.
- 什么?  - 别担心 布鲁 你天生会飞的

669
00:46:30,556 --> 00:46:34,013
And if our featherless friends can do it, how hard can it be?
而且 我们这位没毛的朋友都会飞 你怎么可能做不到呢?

670
00:46:36,455 --> 00:46:38,100
Help me!
救我!

671
00:46:38,562 --> 00:46:39,925
Fun right?
好玩吧?

672
00:46:39,927 --> 00:46:41,843
Yeah, fun.
是啊 很有趣

673
00:46:42,274 --> 00:46:44,878
Okay, I need you two to get closer.
